example:
try:
    ...
except FileNotFoundError:
    if ...:
        raise RuntimeError("...")
    else:
        raise UserWarning("...")



Use instead:


try:
    ...
except FileNotFoundError as exc:
    if ...:
        raise RuntimeError("...") from None
    else:
        raise UserWarning("...") from exc

